</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="ASGBC7A0#Used_as_.22Little_by_Little.22"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Used as "Little by Little"</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="ASGBC7A0#Structure_2"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
